text: Zamora TV is a Venezuelan community television channel. It was created in August 2004 and can be seen in the community of Villa de Cura in the Zamora Municipality of the Aragua State of Venezuela on UHF channel 61. Miguel Ortiz is the legal representative of the foundation that owns this channel.
